<li><a href="/scp-3670">SCP-3670</a> (&quot;Dreamed Corn&quot;) - What, like you could ever want anything more out of life? Som<strong>nomnom</strong>nambulated by Taffeta.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3436">SCP-3436</a> (&quot;ABE&quot;) - A one-way ticket to Skyzone. Written by scpcrnp.</li>
