<li><a href="/scp-3414">SCP-3414</a> (&quot;Beware of Toilet Snake&quot;) - Supposedly it makes this weird <em>hissing</em> noise when you flush it, but eh&#8230; probably not a big deal. Written by minmin.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3279">SCP-3279</a> (&quot;Pareidolia&quot;) - &quot;<em>Retrieval, transportation, and maintenance of all SCP-3279-1 instances may be carried out only by personnel suffering from severe congenital prosopagnosia.</em>&quot; Written by duodude55.</li>
